,{"source":"recjt9WUYw6KLKSeB","target":"recfrXyxhuYOczKTm","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recjt9WUYw6KLKSeB","target":"recIJFRcqI6KbKgXb","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recjt9WUYw6KLKSeB","target":"recJK76HLZSOzxTWW","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recjt9WUYw6KLKSeB","target":"recdm9AlLF01lFAfP","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recjt9WUYw6KLKSeB","target":"recPoImnA7S93jcHx","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recjt9WUYw6KLKSeB","target":"recjdhKnTnRSPWNUo","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recjt9WUYw6KLKSeB","target":"recekTocE5mIkvDEk","label":"event"}],"verses":[{"id":"recWKlwz83GQPAt1d","ref":"Hos.12.1","text":"Ephraim feedeth on wind, and followeth after the east wind: he daily increaseth lies and desolation; and they do make a covenant with the Assyrians, and oil is carried into Egypt.","year":-725},{"id":"recyAc0AaKmhjhFOd","ref":"Hos.12.2","text":"The LORD hath also a controversy with Judah, and will punish Jacob according to his ways; according to his doings will he recompense him.","year":-725},{"id":"reciwyB7UBdtJQoZ4","ref":"Hos.12.3","text":"He took his brother by the heel in the womb, and by his strength he had power with God:","year":-725},{"id":"recCyScCdbAwJ0Xfn","ref":"Hos.12.4","text":"Yea, he had power over the angel, and prevailed: he wept, and made supplication unto him: he found him in Bethel, and there he spake with us;","year":-725},{"id":"recFg0vyADY0D3XLt","ref":"Hos.12.5","text":"Even the LORD God of hosts; the LORD is his memorial.","year":-725},{"id":"recTAalBpPfuiRycq","ref":"Hos.12.6","text":"Therefore turn thou to thy God: keep mercy and judgment, and wait on thy God continually.","year":-725},{"id":"recJ6KtR8w4gZhpWA","ref":"Hos.12.7","text":"He is a merchant, the balances of deceit are in his hand: he loveth to oppress.","year":-725},{"id":"recwQeY2tQZWCcQb3","ref":"Hos.12.8","text":"And Ephraim said, Yet I am become rich, I have found me out substance: in all my labours they shall find none iniquity in me that were sin.","year":-725}]}
